title: Valar Rereadis: The Sworn Sword - Part 4 (w/Jim McGeehin)
description:
Finishing off The Sworn Sword with Something Like a Lawyer!

Topics include: the power of nostalgia, the final boss battle, the difficulty of Dagon, some Redgrass Field-work, the concept of a Medieval Western, loads of innuendo and several other excellent odds and ends.
